|---|---|
| branches | `companyId` |
| departments | `companyId`, `branchId` |
| job-titles | `companyId` |
| hr/employees | `companyId` |
| attendance/check-in-points | `companyId`, `isActive` |
| attendance/check-in-point-links | `companyId`, `employeeId`, `checkInPointId`, `linkActive` |
| leaves/types | `companyId` |
