## 7. RTL & Arabic UI

### 7.1 Root Setup

`src/app/layout.tsx` must have:
```html
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
```

### 7.2 Tailwind — Always Use Logical Properties

| Forbidden | Correct |
|---|---|
| `ml-*` / `mr-*` | `ms-*` / `me-*` |
| `pl-*` / `pr-*` | `ps-*` / `pe-*` |
| `left-*` / `right-*` | `start-*` / `end-*` |
| `text-left` | `text-start` |
| `text-right` | `text-end` |
| `border-l-*` | `border-s-*` |
| `rounded-l-*` | `rounded-s-*` |

Never use `style={{ marginLeft }}`, `style={{ paddingRight }}`, or `style={{ left }}` inline.

### 7.3 Numbers

```typescript
// Currency amounts
new Intl.NumberFormat('ar-SA', { style: 'currency', currency: 'SAR' }).format(amount)

// Plain counts and IDs — Western numerals are acceptable
// Employee codes, system IDs — always Western numerals
```

### 7.4 Dates

```typescript
import { format } from 'date-fns';
import { ar } from 'date-fns/locale';

format(new Date(dateStr), 'dd/MM/yyyy')                        // 24/08/2025
format(new Date(dateStr), 'd MMMM yyyy', { locale: ar })      // ٢٤ أغسطس ٢٠٢٥
```

Hijri calendar: NOT IMPLEMENTED — do not add unless explicitly requested.

### 7.5 Icon Mirroring

```tsx
// Directional icons must flip in RTL
<ChevronRight className="rtl:rotate-180" />
<ArrowRight className="rtl:rotate-180" />

// Non-directional — never flip
<Search /> <Bell /> <User /> <Settings /> <X /> <Check />
```

