## 10. Quick Reference Checklist

Before submitting any new page or feature, verify:

- [ ] API calls are in a service file — not in components or hooks
- [ ] Response accessed with optional chaining (`data?.data?.items`)
- [ ] Salary fields parsed with `parseFloat()` before display or math
- [ ] Permission checked with `useCan()` before showing actions
- [ ] Tailwind uses logical properties (`ms-`, `ps-`, `start-`)
- [ ] `lang="ar" dir="rtl"` on root HTML
- [ ] Zod schema exported alongside its inferred type
- [ ] useMutation has both `onSuccess` (invalidate + toast) and `onError` (toast with details)
- [ ] No UI built for unimplemented backend features
- [ ] Component is under 300 lines

